    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <iconUrl>https://github.com/gep13/ChocolateyPackages/raw/master/calibre/calibre.ico</iconUrl>
    <releaseNotes>
    - New: For a summary of the major changes in calibre between 0.8 and 0.9, see http://calibre-ebook.com/new-in/nine
    - Fixed: KF8 Output: Fix handling of &amp; &lt; and &gt; entities in the text. They were sometimes being incorrectly unescaped.
    - Fixed: Calibre portable: Add a manifest to the portable installer exe to prevent the application compatibility wizard from warning about a possible failed installation on windows 7. Also fixes installer requiring admin privileges on some computers
    - Fixed: EPUB metadata: Fix book producer not being set when updating EPUB metadata
    - Fixed: EPUB metadata: Fix incorrect namespace on the role attribute of <dc:creator> tags when updating the metadata in EPUB
    - Fixed: Get Books: Fix incorrect price retrieval from ebooks.com.
    - Fixed: MTP windows driver: Fix main memory and storage card sometimes swapped
    - Fixed: PDF Output: On windows, remove any embedded fonts before generating the PDF as on windows, Qt generates image based PDFs when embedded fonts are present.
    - Fixed: MTP windows driver: Do not try to connect to unsuitable devices such as the iPhone.
    - Fixed: KF8 Input: Handle files that use non ascii paths/anchor names in the guide entries.
    - New News Source: Pubblico Giornale by iusvar
    - Improved News Source: Monitor Online
    - Improved News Source: El Pais
    - Improved News Source: Chronicle of Higher Education
    - Improved News Source: Baltimore Sun
    - Improved News Source: Mac World
    - Improved News Source: Maximum PC
    - Improved News Source: Financial Times UK
    </releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
</package>
